Second map that I've made, hopefully a little better than my first.  For my clan's GG server as well, but I will allow it on any other GG server.  Because it is for my clan's server, "SE CLAN" is on the wall in the secret room.  There are teleports to and from the secret room, but you have to find those on your own. : )

gg_woodlake can be used in any CS:S server, owned for public or private use. It may NOT be replicated or updated without author's (sE*Guru Janitor*) permission.
